  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Versatile and Robust Mounting Solution",
      "text": "The Universal Antenna Mount produced by Ubiquiti and known by its manufacture part number UB-AM, is is a versatile and robust mounting solution designed to provide a reliable and stable platform for wide range of Ubiquiti devices, particularly those used in wireless point-to-point and point-to-multipoint configurations. The mount features adjustable tilt and swivel capabilities, enabling precise alignment of the antenna or other radio device for optimal signal reception and broadcast. This adjustability is critical for achieving the highest network performance and reducing interference."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Durable Construction and Easy Installation",
      "text": "This universal bracket is made from powder-coated steel to withstand harsh environmental conditions including wind, rain, and extreme temperatures. This durability ensures long-lasting performance and reliability and designed for easy installation, requiring minimal tools. Also, the UB-AM is designed with multiple mounting options, allowing it to be installed on walls or roofs. This versatility ensures that it can be used in a variety of locations to maximize line of sight and signal strength."
    }
  ],
